notifications.title: Appreciation Day
notifications.description: To celebrate our amazing volunteers, we're hosting a special Volunteer Appreciation Day event. We couldn't do what we do without the hard work and dedication of our volunteers.

notifications.title: Kitten Season
notifications.description: It's kitten season again, and that means we'll be seeing a lot of cute and cuddly kittens coming through our doors. While kittens are undeniably adorable, they also require a lot of care.

notifications.title: Adopt a Pet
notifications.description: We have dogs, cats, and other small animals looking for their forever homes, and we'd love to help you find your perfect match.

notifications.title: Virus Awareness
notifications.description: Did you know that cats can contract Feline Immunodeficiency Virus (FIV)? This virus attacks a cat's immune system and can cause a number of health issues.

notifications.title: Hurricane Relief
notifications.description: We're working with local shelters and organizations to rescue animals in need, provide medical care, and help reunite lost pets with their owners.

notifications.title: Clear the Shelters
notifications.description: Join us for Clear the Shelters Day and help us find homes for all of our furry friends! We're waiving adoption fees and offering special discounts on pet supplies.

notifications.title: Holiday Donations
notifications.description: Help us make the holidays a little brighter for our furry friends by participating in our holiday donation drive.

notifications.title: Valentine's Day
notifications.description: Fall in love with a new furry friend this Valentine's Day! Join us for our adoption event and meet some of our adoptable pets.

notifications.title: Puppy Socialization
notifications.description: Is your new puppy in need of socialization? Join us for our puppy socialization class, where your furry friend can learn valuable skills and meet other puppies.

notifications.title: Summer Safety
notifications.description: Summer can be a fun time for pets, but it can also be dangerous. Make sure your furry friends stay safe in the summer heat by providing plenty of fresh water and shade.

notifications.title: National Dog Day
notifications.description: Celebrate National Dog Day with a new furry friend! Join us for our adoption event and meet some of our adoptable dogs. We'll have treats for both you and your furry friend.

notifications.title: Photos with Santa
notifications.description: It's that time of year again! Bring your furry friend to our Pet Photos with Santa event and get a keepsake photo of your pet with jolly old St. Nick.

notifications.title: Foster Orientation
notifications.description: Attend our Foster Orientation and learn all about our foster program. Our foster parents play a critical role in helping our animals find their forever homes.

notifications.title: Kitty Playtime
notifications.description: Join us for Kitty Playtime, where you can spend quality time with our adoptable cats and kittens. Our playtime sessions are a great way to get to know our feline friends and see their personalities.
